<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>결제 상세 | Seoyeon Tour</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: #f8f7f4; }
        .nav-link { color: #555 !important; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .nav-link:hover { color: #000 !important; }
        .detail-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            padding: 36px;
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 100px auto 60px;
        }
        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #aaa;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .product-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
        }
        .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .info-row span:first-child { color: #888; }
        .info-row span:last-child { font-weight: 500; color: #333; }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 3px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .status-paid { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; }
        .status-pending { background: #fff8e1; color: #f57f17; }
        .status-cancelled { background: #fce4ec; color: #c62828; }
        .total-box {
            background: #f8f7f4;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .total-box span:first-child { color: #888; font-size: 0.88rem; }
        .total-box span:last-child { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a2e; }
        .btn-back {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #888;
            background: transparent;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-back:hover { border-color: #1a1a2e; color: #1a1a2e; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white shadow-sm fixed-top px-4">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">SEOYEON TOUR</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMenu">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMenu">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto gap-2">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/introduce">소개</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/event">이벤트</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/honeymoon-europe">허니문-유럽</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/honeymoon-resort">허니문-휴양지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/group">단체여행</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/package">패키지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/reviews">후기</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contact">온라인문의</a></li>
                <% if (user) { %>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link fw-bold text-dark" href="/mypage"><%= user.name %>님</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/mypage">마이페이지</a></li>
                <% if (user.role === 'admin') { %>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-warning" href="/admin">어드민</a></li>
                <% } %>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a></li>
                <% } else { %>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/login">로그인</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/signup-page">회원가입</a></li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="detail-card">
        <p class="section-label">My Payments</p>
        <h5 class="section-title">결제 상세 내역</h5>

        <img src="/images/<%= payment.image %>" class="product-img" alt="<%= payment.product_name %>">

        <div class="info-row">
            <span>상품명</span>
            <span><%= payment.product_name %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>여행지</span>
            <span><%= payment.destination %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>여행 기간</span>
            <span><%= payment.duration %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>예약 인원</span>
            <span><%= payment.quantity %>명</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>결제 수단</span>
            <span><%= payment.pay_method || '-' %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>결제 일시</span>
            <span><%= new Date(payment.paid_at).toLocaleString('ko-KR') %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>주문 번호</span>
            <span style="font-size:0.78rem; color:#aaa;"><%= payment.order_id %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span>결제 상태</span>
            <span>
                <% if (payment.payment_status === 'paid') { %>
                <span class="status-badge status-paid">결제 완료</span>
                <% } else if (payment.payment_status === 'pending') { %>
                <span class="status-badge status-pending">결제 대기</span>
                <% } else { %>
                <span class="status-badge status-cancelled">취소</span>
                <% } %>
            </span>
        </div>

        <div class="total-box">
            <span>총 결제 금액</span>
            <span><%= Number(payment.total_price).toLocaleString() %>원</span>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 d-flex justify-content-between">
            <a href="/mypage" class="btn-back">← 마이페이지로</a>
            <a href="/product/<%= payment.product_id %>" class="btn-back">상품 보기 →</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="py-5 text-center text-muted small border-top">
        <p class="fw-medium text-dark mb-1">SEOYEON TOUR</p>
        <p>대표자: 원서연, 정유진</p>
        <p>Tel: 010-2987-7368 · Email: angelo2001@naver.com</p>
        <p class="mt-3">© 2025 Seoyeon Tour. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
